---
By: Theo Bovet
Locus:
  Page: 90
  Verse: 12
Tags:
  - Death
---
My present experience is that Eternal Life does not begin after death, but
that we start living it now; only it is masked by our daily cares, and it
is only on contact with death, perhaps, that we discover it. God is not a
God of the dead, but of the living, since for him they are all living.
